# User Age API

A production-style RESTful API built with **Go**, **Fiber**, **PostgreSQL**, and **SQLC** that manages users and calculates age dynamically from date of birth.

## Features

* Create, Read, Update, and Delete (CRUD) users
* Dynamic age calculation using Go's `time` package
* PostgreSQL database integration
* SQLC-generated type-safe database layer
* Request validation using `go-playground/validator`
* Structured logging with Uber Zap
* Request logging middleware
* Request ID middleware for traceability
* Pagination support
* Unit testing
* Docker & Docker Compose support
* Clean Architecture (Handler → Service → Repository)

---

## Tech Stack

| Technology     | Purpose                       |
| -------------- | ----------------------------- |
| Go             | Backend Language              |
| Fiber          | HTTP Framework                |
| PostgreSQL     | Database                      |
| SQLC           | Type-safe SQL code generation |
| Uber Zap       | Structured Logging            |
| Validator      | Input Validation              |
| Docker         | Containerization              |
| Docker Compose | Multi-container orchestration |

